How Bout It
===========

serves 2
--------

1 1/2 oz	Genepy
1 1/2 oz 	Bonal
1 oz		St George's Terroir Gin
1/2 0z		Fairy Dust by 510.  substitute with absynth 1/4 - 1/5 oz
juice of 1 fresh kumquat
  - or -
3/4 oz lemon or lime juice

shaken with ice.  serve up.  garnish with kumquat rind



serves 1
--------

1 oz	Genepy
1 oz 	Bonal
3/4 oz	St George's Terroir Gin
1/4 0z	absynth
juice of 1 fresh kumquat

